\title{Simple Definition for The Real Numbers}
\taxon{Definition}
\p{To provide an initial definition for #{\mathbb{R}}, we assume that #{\mathbb{R}} is an ordered [field](000G) which contains #{\mathbb{Q}} as a subfield. We also require that it contain no gaps between rational numbers. We accomplish this second requirement via the axiom of completeness.}
\transclude{000I}